ergism', 'Caution is advised when brentuximab is used with potent CYP450 3A4 inhibitors (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/47145/', '', 'Citalopram, Sertraline, Maprotiline, Fluoxetine, St. John''s Wort, Vortioxetine, Levomilnacipran, Doxepin, Isocarboxazid, Viloxazine, Amoxapine, More', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Amivantamab, More', 1767369485);
